{"id": "art-374", "label": "Art. 374", "title": "Art. 374: Exercitarea raporturilor de serviciu", "slug": "art-374", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 374: Exercitarea raporturilor de serviciu </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Raporturile de serviciu se nasc\n&#351;i se exercit&#259; pe baza actului administrativ de numire, emis în\ncondi&#355;iile legii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Exercitarea raporturilor de\nserviciu se realizeaz&#259; pe perioad&#259; nedeterminat&#259; sau\ndeterminat&#259; în condi&#355;iile prevederilor din prezentul cod.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1156066829\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1381\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1156066829\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Raporturile de serviciu ale func&#355;ionarilor publici\nse pot exercita &#351;i în regim de telemunc&#259;, în condi&#355;iile\nprev&#259;zute de prezentul cod, precum &#351;i în regim de munc&#259; la\ndomiciliu, potrivit prevederilor Legii nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>53/2003</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, republicat&#259;, cu modific&#259;rile &#351;i\ncomplet&#259;rile ulterioare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1121165770\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1380\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1121165770\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Conduc&#259;torii autorit&#259;&#355;ilor &#351;i\ninstitu&#355;iilor publice pot stabili prin act administrativ &#351;i alte\nmoduri de organizare flexibil&#259; a timpului de lucru, potrivit art. 118\nalin. (7) din Legea nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>53/2003</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, republicat&#259;, cu modific&#259;rile &#351;i\ncomplet&#259;rile ulterioare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_523416670\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1379\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_523416670\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Activitatea desf&#259;&#351;urat&#259; în regim de telemunc&#259;\nse bazeaz&#259; pe acordul de voin&#355;&#259; al p&#259;r&#355;ilor &#351;i se\nrealizeaz&#259; ca urmare a aprob&#259;rii de c&#259;tre conduc&#259;torul\nautorit&#259;&#355;ii sau institu&#355;iei publice a solicit&#259;rii\nfunc&#355;ionarului public.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1088619718\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1378\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1088619718\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Conduc&#259;torii autorit&#259;&#355;ilor &#351;i\ninstitu&#355;iilor publice stabilesc prin act administrativ structurile din\ncadrul acestora, activit&#259;&#355;ile, precum &#351;i posturile pentru care\nse poate aproba desf&#259;&#351;urarea activit&#259;&#355;ii în regim de\ntelemunc&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1295526829\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1377\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1295526829\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Durata activit&#259;&#355;ii desf&#259;&#351;urate în\nregim de telemunc&#259; nu poate dep&#259;&#351;i 5 zile pe lun&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_524412399\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1376\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_524412399\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Desf&#259;&#351;urarea\nactivit&#259;&#355;ii în regim de telemunc&#259; se poate aproba pentru:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_767486246\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1375\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_767486246\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)func&#355;ionarii publici care au copii cu vârsta de\npân&#259; la 11 ani;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2124597811\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1374\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2124597811\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)func&#355;ionarii publici care acord&#259; îngrijire unei\nrude, în accep&#355;iunea art. 153<sup>1</sup> alin. (4) din Legea nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>53/2003</span><span style='color:black'>,\nrepublicat&#259;, cu modific&#259;rile &#351;i complet&#259;rile ulterioare, cu\ncare locuie&#351;te în aceea&#351;i gospod&#259;rie;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2071659809\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1373\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2071659809\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)func&#355;ionarii publici care au o stare de\ns&#259;n&#259;tate care nu le permite deplasarea la sediul\nautorit&#259;&#355;ii sau institu&#355;iei publice, din cauze determinate de\nunele boli grave, ori în situa&#355;ie de graviditate, dovedite prin adeverin&#355;&#259;\nmedical&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1824368969\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1372\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1824368969\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)func&#355;ionarii publici care desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259;\nactivit&#259;&#355;i dintre cele stabilite de conduc&#259;torul\nautorit&#259;&#355;ii sau institu&#355;iei publice ca putând fi realizate în\nregim de telemunc&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1227769044\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1371\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1227769044\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Func&#355;ionarii\npublici care î&#351;i desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; activitatea în regim de\ntelemunc&#259; au urm&#259;toarele obliga&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_493122678\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1370\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_493122678\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)s&#259; dispun&#259; de toate mijloacele necesare\nîndeplinirii atribu&#355;iilor care le revin potrivit fi&#351;ei postului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_354641141\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1369\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_354641141\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)s&#259; r&#259;spund&#259; la orice solicitare\nreferitoare la activitatea profesional&#259; primit&#259; de la superiorii\nierarhici, în timpul programului de lucru, transmis&#259; prin mijloace de\ncomunicare la distan&#355;&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1291335448\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1368\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1291335448\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)s&#259; respecte normele cuprinse în Regulamentul de\norganizare &#351;i func&#355;ionare al institu&#355;iei, Regulamentul intern,\nnormele cu privire la protec&#355;ia datelor cu caracter personal &#351;i alte\nnorme &#351;i proceduri specifice aplicabile, dup&#259; caz.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_957967956\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1367\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_957967956\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Autorit&#259;&#355;ile\n&#351;i institu&#355;iile publice la nivelul c&#259;rora exist&#259;\nfunc&#355;ionari publici care î&#351;i desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; activitatea în\nregim de telemunc&#259; au urm&#259;toarele obliga&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1774395955\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1366\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1774395955\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)s&#259; verifice activitatea func&#355;ionarilor publici,\nîn principal prin utilizarea tehnologiei informa&#355;iei &#351;i\ncomunica&#355;iilor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_670653045\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1365\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_670653045\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)s&#259; asigure modalitatea de eviden&#355;iere a orelor\nde munc&#259; prestate în regim de telemunc&#259; de c&#259;tre\nfunc&#355;ionarii publici;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1885036292\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1364\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1885036292\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)s&#259; se asigure c&#259; func&#355;ionarii publici\nde&#355;in mijloacele aferente tehnologiei informa&#355;iei &#351;i\ncomunica&#355;iilor &#351;i echipamentele de munc&#259; func&#355;ionale,\nsigure &#351;i necesare prest&#259;rii muncii sau s&#259; pun&#259; la\ndispozi&#355;ia func&#355;ionarilor publici aceste mijloace &#351;i\nechipamente;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1236699622\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1363\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1236699622\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)s&#259; se asigure c&#259; func&#355;ionarii publici\nprimesc o instruire suficient&#259; &#351;i adecvat&#259; în domeniul\nsecurit&#259;&#355;ii &#351;i s&#259;n&#259;t&#259;&#355;ii în munc&#259;, în\nspecial sub form&#259; de informa&#355;ii &#351;i instruc&#355;iuni de lucru\nprivind utilizarea echipamentelor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2078992843\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1362\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2078992843\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(11)Pe durata exercit&#259;rii activit&#259;&#355;ii în\nregim de telemunc&#259; sau a muncii la domiciliu, func&#355;ionarii publici\nbeneficiaz&#259; de toate drepturile recunoscute prin lege, cu excep&#355;ia\nsporului pentru condi&#355;ii de munc&#259; grele, v&#259;t&#259;m&#259;toare\nsau periculoase.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}